pe oleracea) and timber. They should also fight illegal timber exploitation that threatens the fauna and flora of those biodiverse forests.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Castro, Isai Jorge De", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Michalski, Fernanda", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/f7232619299c9820319723c2c6e424dc", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/6fa4eabcb3626671406d2d2112ca06773739c6cf714bbe9687284cb05918aa4e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/IIGVRQR7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/IIGVRQR7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/94188dec857e239657d8f301885e70a6!/b70422-72907", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "title": "Biota Neotropica", "volume": "15"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/f7232619299c9820319723c2c6e424dc"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:IIGVRQR7"}, {"identifier": "10.1590/1676-06032015016814"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13463958"}}]}}, "title": "Bats of a varzea forest in the estuary of the Amazon River, state o